eMobile":34},{"value":89},{"mediaType":37,"url":38,"opacity":66,"options":40,"svgCode":38,"videoUrl":38,"videoThumbnail":38,"videoLoop":41},{"value":91},"column",{"value":93},"center",{"value":95},"inherit",{"value":41},{"value":98},[],{"value":100},2,"c-column","1st Column",1,{"extra":105,"id":77,"tagName":113,"class":114,"meta":126},{"visibility":106,"text":108,"nodeId":110,"customClass":111},{"value":107},{"hideMobile":38,"hideDesktop":38},{"value":109},"\u003Ch2>\u003Cstrong>Effective Date: 01/03/2025\u003C/strong>\u003C/h2>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>At Full Arch Sales Experts, accessible from \u003Ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://fullarchsalesexperts.com\">https://fullarchsalesexperts.com\u003C/a>, your privacy is a top priority.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website and interact with our services, including course purchases and content hosted through Teachable.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>1. Information We Collect\u003C/p>\u003Cp>We may collect the following types of information:\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Personal Information: Your name, email address, and other contact details when you voluntarily submit forms, sign up for updates, or contact us.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Payment Information: When purchasing courses, payment details are processed securely through Teachable.com. We do not store or access your credit card or banking information.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>2. How We Use Your Information\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>We use your information to:\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>Provide and manage course access via Teachable.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Respond to your inquiries and provide support.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Send important updates related to courses or content.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>3. Third-Party Services\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Our courses and checkout process are hosted on Teachable.com. Your use of Teachable is also governed by their Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>We encourage you to review their policies at \u003Ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://teachable.com/privacy-policy\">https://teachable.com/privacy-policy\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>4. Cookies\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Our website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can choose to disable cookies in your browser settings, though it may impact some site features.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>5. Data Security\u003C/p>\u003Cp>We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>However, no online platform is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>6. Your Rights\u003C/p>\u003Cp>You have the right to:\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Access the personal information we hold about you.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Request correction or deletion of your data.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Opt out of marketing emails at any time using the unsubscribe link.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Ch2>To exercise these rights, \u003Ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://fullarchsalesexperts.com/discovery-call\">Let's talk today\u003C/a>\u003C/h2>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>7. Children's Privacy\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Our site and courses are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>8. Changes to This Policy\u003C/p>\u003Cp>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>\u003C/h2>\u003Cp>9. Contact Us\u003C/p>\u003Ch2>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, Please contact us at \u003Cstrong>stacy@fullarchsalesexperts.com\u003C/strong>.\u003C/h2>","csub-heading-EFeN-cXKqv",{"value":112},[],"c-sub-heading",{"borders":115,"borderRadius":116,"radius